{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/popularitas-k-pop-dalam-dunia-musik-amerika/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Popularitas K-Pop dalam Dunia Musik Amerika","content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sekitar lima atau tujuh tahun yang lalu, muncul banyak opini dan artikel dengan pertanyaan “bisakah trend musik K-pop menembus pasar Amerika?” Sekarang kalau kita coba perhatiin acara musik di Amerika (Billboard Music Award misalnya), kita bisa menemukan jawabannya dengan mudah. Berkat kemajuan akses internet dan penyebaran informasi yang cepat, perkembangan musik K-pop di Amerika makin besar. Bahkan gak hanya tentang musik, idol, dan drama Korea aja. Tapi juga produk kecantikan, fashion, bahkan bahasa Korea makin banyak dipelajari oleh penggemar K-pop di Amerika. Kalau kita melihat balik ke lima tahun lalu, rasanya musik K-pop gak begitu diminati oleh pasaran musik barat. Gak sedikit juga yang menganggap K-pop boyband sebenarnya bukan penyanyi yang benar-benar punya <em>talent</em>, tapi lebih menunjukkan penampilan visual mereka.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_27347\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-27347\" data-attachment-id=\"27347\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/popularitas-k-pop-dalam-dunia-musik-amerika/attachment/isi-2-1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-2-1-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"source 2: pinterest.com(Jisoo member Blackpink)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;source 2: pinterest.com(Jisoo member Blackpink)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-2-1-1.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-2-1-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-27347\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-2-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"source 2: pinterest.com(Jisoo member Blackpink)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-27347\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">source 2: pinterest.com(Jisoo member Blackpink)</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_41089\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41089\" data-attachment-id=\"41089\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/popularitas-k-pop-dalam-dunia-musik-amerika/attachment/eunwooastro/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/eunwooastro.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"source 3: pinterest.com(Eunwoo member boyband ASTRO)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;source 3: pinterest.com(Eunwoo member boyband ASTRO)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/eunwooastro-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/eunwooastro.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-41089\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/eunwooastro.jpg\" alt=\"source 3: pinterest.com(Eunwoo member boyband ASTRO)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/eunwooastro.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/eunwooastro-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-41089\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">source 3: pinterest.com(Eunwoo member boyband ASTRO)</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Berpikir kalau K-pop itu sebenarnya lebih menunjukkan visual, sebenarnya gak salah sama sekali! Idol di Korea memang dibuat secantik dan terlihat sesempurna mungkin secara visual. Fashion look juga berperan penting untuk penampilan idol Korea. Tapi semuanya gak hanya tentang visual aja kok. Mereka juga melalui proses trainee yang lama, memakan waktu bertahun-tahun untuk latihan vokal dan dance, dan baru kemudian didebutkan. Musik ‘K-pop’ ini sebenarnya agak rancu. Karena kebanyakan orang secara global berpendapat kalau musik dari Korea ya K-pop. Padahal genre musik yang mereka tunjukkan gak hanya pop aja. Ada Hip Hop, ada EDM, R&amp;B, ada juga band Indie. Dan meskipun punya banyak perbedaan dengan proses menjadi seorang artis dan mengeluarkan album antara Korea dan musik barat, Idol Korea juga memiliki talenta dan bakat.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_27353\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-27353\" data-attachment-id=\"27353\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/popularitas-k-pop-dalam-dunia-musik-amerika/attachment/isi-4-1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-4-1-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"source 4: pinterest.com (exo)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;source 4: pinterest.com (exo)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-4-1-1.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-4-1-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-27353\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-4-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"source 4: pinterest.com (exo)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-27353\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">source 4: pinterest.com (exo)</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Awal perkembangan musik K-pop di Amerika sebenarnya sebatas dari internet aja, karena gak mudah mencari album K-pop di outlet musik. Penggemar musik K-pop punya komunitas di Facebook, lalu berkembang ke Twitter dan Youtube, Tumblr, dan Instagram. Saat video musik K-pop mendapat banyak viewers di Youtube dalam waktu yang singkat, orang-orang jadi penasaran untuk melihat videonya. Mulai dari situlah Amerika dan dunia musik barat mulai <em>aware </em>dengan popularitas musik Korea. Setelah sukses di Asia, agensi Korea yang menyadari kalau musiknya sudah diterima di barat mulai memperluas marketing untuk artis mereka. Contohnya dengan mengontrak idol menjadi model kosmetik, yang nantinya produk kosmetik itu akan diekspor ke banyak negara luar Korea.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_41090\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-41090\" data-attachment-id=\"41090\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/popularitas-k-pop-dalam-dunia-musik-amerika/attachment/jihoowannaone/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/jihoowannaone.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"source 5: pinterest.com (Jihoon from Wanna One)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;source 5: pinterest.com (Jihoon from Wanna One)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/jihoowannaone-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/jihoowannaone.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-41090\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/jihoowannaone.jpg\" alt=\"source 5: pinterest.com (Jihoon from Wanna One)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/jihoowannaone.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/jihoowannaone-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-41090\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">source 5: pinterest.com (Jihoon from Wanna One)</p></div></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Tur konser maupun fanmeeting juga dibuat di Amerika bahkan Eropa. Tiket konser K-pop juga sering sold out dalam waktu singkat. Hal ini menunjukkan kalau K-pop bukan hal yang asing lagi untuk dunia barat. Belum lama ini boyband Korea, BTS menerima penghargaan Top Social Artist Award. BTS menang melawan Justin Bieber, Ariana Grande, Selena Gomez, dan Shawn Mendes loh! Kebayang kan ada berapa banyak fans BTS yang mendukung di media sosial? Selain dikabarkan bakal merilis single featuring The Chainsmoker, BTS juga baru aja shooting di LateLate Show milik James Corden di Amerika. Mulai sekarang, Tren K-pop bukan lagi cuma tentang  ‘Gangnam Style’ yang sempat populer di Amerika. Tapi lebih tentang <em>talent</em>, pengakuan, dan apresiasi tentang genre musik asal Korea.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_27350\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-27350\" data-attachment-id=\"27350\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/popularitas-k-pop-dalam-dunia-musik-amerika/attachment/isi-3-1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-3-1-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"source 6: celebmix.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;source 6: celebmix.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-3-1-1.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-3-1-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-27350\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ISI-3-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"source 6: celebmix.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-27350\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">source 6: celebmix.com</p></div></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"f7ead152-da05-50cf-8085-458ddd31b154"}}}